<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="1331">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-cheng-chun-18" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-cheng-chun-18" class="zg-link" title="王承淳">王承淳</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$an-yi-e-mo-shi-k" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/an-yi-e-mo-shi-k" class="zg-link" title="黯熠恶魔使k">黯熠恶魔使k</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wei-da-de-you-yu-zhan-shi" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wei-da-de-you-yu-zhan-shi" class="zg-link" title="伟大的鱿鱼战士">伟大的鱿鱼战士</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


